'''''Hero, Return to Dawn in Mortality''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[As Tomorrow Became Yesterday]].

==Steps==
# Enter the Ruins of Time and begin the final "Flame-Chase Journey"
# Gather the "Last Titans" and prepare to face Irontomb
# Travel with Cyrene to the depths of the ruins.
# Gather the "Last Titans" and prepare to face Irontomb
# Try using the power of Time to move the giant boulder blocking the way
# Failed attempt. Perhaps the power of Time belongs elsewhere...
# Move the giant boulder blocking the path with the help of Oronyx's Prayer
# Continue forward into the depths of the ruins
# Gather the "Last Titans" and prepare to face Irontomb
# Attempt to initiate the ceremony and take away the Wish of Worldbearing
# Collect three wishes
# Carry the wishes and take away Worldbearing's mark
# Gather the "Last Titans" and prepare to face Irontomb
# Check the recollections and records about Phainon in the room
# Bid farewell to the two avatars of Tribios, Gate of Infinity, and venture deeper into the void
# Find the other half of the Worldbearing mark
# Initiate the ceremony and break the Despair of Worldbearing
# Shatter the three parts of despair
# Extinguish despair and take the other half of the Worldbearing mark
# Follow the "Blank Wish" to the spirit basin to dissolve the "Wish" and "Despair" of the Worldbearer.
# Talk to Blank Wish and send the Worldbearer's wishes to tomorrow
# Gather the "Last Titans" and prepare to face Irontomb
# Travel with Cyrene to the depths of the ruins.
# Attempt to initiate the ceremony and take away the Wish of Worldbearing
# Carry the wishes and take away Worldbearing's mark
# Initiate the ceremony and break the Despair of Worldbearing
# Extinguish despair and take the other half of the Worldbearing mark

